track_notes: 3 mile hike with 1380 EG.  Trailhead is at Newfound Gap on Hwy 441 (35.611, -83.426).  Large parking lot, but can get very busy.  Head north on the AT for 2.7 miles, take a left on the Boulevard Trail and after a short distance take a right on the trail to the Jumpoff.  The summit of Mt Kephart is 1/4 mile before you get to the Jumpoff, which I do recommend for the views.  Summit is along the trail with only a small overgrown clearing.  This was a very busy trail on a summer weekend.
AT to Boulevard to Jump Off trails leading to Mt. Kephart.
